reviewText: Compr este video porque no hay muchos videos en espaol para nios en este pas y cre que le iba a gustar a mi hija de 3 aos. / I bought this video because there are not many videos in Spanish for kids in this country and I thought my 3-year-old would like it.  Supongo que es para muchachos ms grandes pero mi hija y yo lo encontramos aburrido. / I guess it's for older kids but my daughter and I found it boring.
